<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- halumã nuh̊di sub̊ḥanā
 lạis̊mi ạl̊masīḥi rabĩnā
 fah̊wa ạlãdẖī ạảḥabãnā
 waqad̊ faday̱ nufūsanā

[V2]
 2- wah̊wa surūru ạlậbi min̊
 qab̊li wujūdi ạl̊ʿālamīn̊
 ʿin̊dahu kāna ṣāniʿaⁿạ
 ladẖãtahu fī kulĩ ḥīn̊

[V3]
 3- lakin̊ ại̹lay̱ ạảʿ̊māqi
 ạlạảr̊ḍi nazala baʿ̊da ạl̊mamāt̊
 waqāma ạảẙḍaⁿạ ṣāʿidaⁿạ
 faẘqa jamīʿi ạlsãmāwāt̊

[V4]
 4- fālậna ṣir̊nā qidĩysīn̊
 wabilạ laẘmiⁿ fī ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ qad̊ wafay̱ duyūnanā
 jamīʿahā ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊

[V5]
 5- wālậbu qad̊ bārakanā
 fīhi bikulĩ ạl̊barakāt̊
 wabiạs̊mihi ạảẙḍaⁿạ nanāl̊
 kulã ạl̊ʿaṭāyā wāl̊hibāt̊</lyrics>
<title>hlm nhd sbḥnạ</title>
</song>